  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-local-id=\"dfd08e0b4d30\" data-macro-id=\"60a889d6-3dad-4032-a2a4-9458c9fc68fa\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p local-id=\"5f955a3c1102\">Note: Cryptomatte is not currently implemented in XPU / R27 </p></div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"1591\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433097887&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1591&amp;height=894\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433097887&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"894\" data-width=\"1591\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642098\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642079\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"9bd23e3f-74ae-4aa9-a625-8ab96fe776e0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433097887&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1591&amp;height=894 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433097887&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1591&amp;height=894 1x\"></span><p local-id=\"64ca69dc9d11\" /><p local-id=\"05a8b141c988\">Using the <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542235274/PxrCryptomatte\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrCryptomatte </a>workflow, you can output IDs in Solaris for easy selection in a compositing application, which you can then use that selection as a mask to make changes selectively in post-production.</p><p local-id=\"afa58db079f0\">PxrCryptomatte is supplied as a<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/RFH27/544642120/Solaris+Sample+and+Display+Filters\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Sample Filter</a> plugin. As such, the output for Cryptomatte is stored as a separate EXR file from your beauty or denoise outputs. Please note an OpenEXR is required to store the values correctly.</p><p local-id=\"796ecbebbc93\" /><hr local-id=\"a6e5fe8e6df2\"/><p local-id=\"55ac9c5ffdd4\">See <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RFH27/pages/544642120/Solaris+Sample+and+Display+Filters\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642120\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Solaris Sample and Display Filters</a> to create and assign a PxrCryptomatter sample filter.</p><hr local-id=\"6af577d3308e\"/><p local-id=\"171b2419fbad\">The above example will output a separate Cryptomatte exr file and assign a unique matId for each material in the Solaris scene.<br/><br/>Once rendered, you can then use software like The Foundry's Nuke to isolate a particular material or object in the scene.  In this example, we have selected the back wall in the studio, using the Cryptomatte Nuke Gizmo<br/><br/><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433097887&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433097887&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642101\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642079\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"972f9cf0-1ef8-4b18-b868-22e96a8ca79b\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/><br/>And from there, we can use that output as a mask to drive a ColorCorrect node to gamma-correct that particular part of the image, enabling the foreground elements to stand out further from the background.</p><p local-id=\"dab73eb48c9e\" /><p local-id=\"2ae775c982c4\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433098133&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544642079/RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754433098133&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544642104\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_Solaris_Cryptomatte_image3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544642079\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"7\" data-media-id=\"9fba9f65-771a-4dec-96bd-481fe73c7c66\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/>More detailed information about the Cryptomatte Sample filter can be found on the dedicated <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://rmanwiki-27.pixar.com/space/REN27/542235274/PxrCryptomatte\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrCryptomatte </a>page<br/><br/></p>"
    }
  },
